Aid breaks down the immune system and puts you at risk of dying from a year cold . symptoms include : anal bleeding , rash , and dryness , dispersing of blood orally , dried mouth and lips , violent involuntary shaking , rapid weight loss , and eventual death . Ways to avoid it is safe sex , not using heroine , protecting open wounds , and knowing your partner . Aids is transmitted through blood , breast milk , or semen .
